name: Brushed In Gold
description:
It was at least 10pm when we started creating this image, and we already had a long day of making art together.  Somehow these two still wanted to get brushed in gold paint and adorned with bangly bits and headdresses. Adolf is much sweeter than he looks, and Muza is a creative bad ass who designed the outfit she is wearing. I made her body paint his thighs cause it made me nervous ;-)
